<h2>F&M Joy Card</h2>
<p>
To run the COMX emulator with the F&M Joy card select 'f&m.joycard.bin' in any available slot (CARD 1 if no expansion box is used), see example below (yellow ellipse):
</p>
<p>
<IMG SRC="images/comx_joy.png" BORDER="0">
</p>
<p>
The F&M Joy Card will only work with software designed for this card, like F&M Pit Stop, Joy Tekenen, Activate Joycard and Joy in basic.
</p>
